{
  "stem": "812.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "We were always talking about the B's-- the three B's, things that started with the letter B-- a bath, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] bread and butter.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And there was another B, but I think those were the most important things.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And-- and it's-- I-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I always can't say enough about my mother.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "It was really her inner strength and her foresight that saw us through.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "She is one remarkable lady, as she is today, and not a bitter person, not angry, and very positive.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And she instilled that positive outlook on life to my brother, and particularly to me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] my leg on the train, of course, was in terrible shape.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "It was oozing with pus, and lice were crawling all in it and out it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And it was bloody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And it was-- it was very bad.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "It was a deep hole.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And there was absolutely no-- no medical attention, of course, whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "As I said, the Russians-- no, I did not say that the Russians then liberated us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "The Germans fled.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "And the Russians came onboard the train and led us to a nearby village by the name of Trobitz that was in the area of Leipzig in eastern Germany.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Again, during these 13 days aboard the train, thousands died.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "Those who died were-- had to be left along the tracks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] These were horrible sights.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "It's something that I-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I just push in the back of my mind.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "It just seems as though all of this happened-- just like in another lifetime, as though it really didn't happen to me.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
